---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About" description="How Prompt Pantry works.">
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-10">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-charcoal mb-6">About Prompt Pantry</h1>

    <div class="recipe-prose text-warm-gray">
      <p class="text-lg text-charcoal">
        Prompt Pantry is a family recipe collection. Every dish is AI-generated, but each one
        is built from real techniques and real culinary knowledge.
      </p>

      <h2>How recipes are made</h2>
      <p>
        Each recipe starts with a deep dive into renowned versions of a dish — professional techniques,
        chef insights, regional variations, and the culinary science behind what makes it work. That's
        then synthesized into an original recipe that combines the best approaches into something
        cohesive and practical.
      </p>

      <h2>Why this exists</h2>
      <p>
        Because good recipes shouldn't require scrolling past a 2,000-word essay about someone's
        trip to Tuscany. Prompt Pantry gives you clearly written recipes with
        useful tools — serving scalers, ingredient checklists, step timers, and cook mode for
        hands-free use in the kitchen.
      </p>

      <h2>How to use this site</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Serving scaler</strong> — Adjust the number of servings and all ingredient
          quantities update automatically.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Ingredient checkboxes</strong> — Check off ingredients as you prep them
          for easy mise en place tracking.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Cook mode</strong> — A distraction-free, step-by-step view that keeps
          your screen awake while you cook.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Step timers</strong> — Tap any timer in a recipe step to start a countdown
          right in the page.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Technique guides</strong> — Linked explanations of fundamental cooking
          techniques referenced throughout recipes.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
